  ('locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-00192', 'locality-d0d1b9a2', 'locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-113-f6c431ec', 'sub-locality-d0d1b9a2-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '若社會中選民面對x、y、z三個不同議案的偏好排列順序，以“>”表示偏好優於，分別為： ㉑x>z>y有35%的選民 ㉒y>x>z有33%的選民 ㉓z>y>x有32%的選民 若選舉議程設定由x、z兩案先投票，勝出者與y案讓選民再投票，以選出最後方案；最後勝出 者，會是那一個方案？', '["x", "y", "z", "會出現循環多數決"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8d609fba72f4", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8a283bc032f5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113200", "c": "504", "s": "1209", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "財政學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
